# Babel
Babel is used as a transpiler for JSX element
Babel is javascript compiler
Below is how it is converted to html 
Babel  converts JSX to React.createElement , that's how browser can understand code
(JSX => React.createElement => ReactElement.(JSObject) => HtmlElement(render))

JSx uses camelcase to attributes eg: className

